<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2008/10/09/free-culture/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Free Culture">Free Culture</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"></p>
<p>If you want to know more about how the American copyright system became broken, and why instead of fostering creative innovation like it used to, it now suppresses it, read Free Culture by Lawrence Lessig. Heck, read it anyway. You can buy the printed book or download it for free. It illuminates everything Sita Sings the Blues is up against, and why you should care.</p>
<p class="wp-flattr-button">If you want to know more about how the American copyright system became broken, and why instead of fostering creative innovation like it used to, it now suppresses
