<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2008/10/01/best-script-in-athens/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Best Script in Athens!">Best Script in Athens!</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>Sita Sings the Blues won Best Script at the Athens International Film Festival. It&#8217;s an honor I credit to Sita&#8217;s talented collaborators, especially Manish Acharya, Aseem Chhabra and Bhavana Nagulapally, who improvised all the narration.</p>
<p>Sita also received an Honorable Mention for &#8220;Best Animated Feature Film&#8221; at the Ottawa Animation Festival.</p>
<p>So the film is in excellent health, even while I am a quivering wreck.</p>
